title: Ohms
description:
Developed with Dr. Bobak Mosadegh, Director of the Dalio Institute at Weill Cornell Medicine, Ohms helps you understand your daily activities - sleep, exercise, and much more - to transform your health and mood. 
Get daily scores, goals, and correlations for your activities. Ohms is for everyone from those looking to start a healthier and happier journey to enthusiasts with wearables.
